WorkItem.Description:
Setting:
RibbonSplitButton myRibbonSplitButton = new RibbonSplitButton();
myRibbonSplitButton.ToolTipDescription = "test"; 
Shows up fine on mouse over. But:
RibbonSplitButton myRibbonSplitButton = new RibbonSplitButton();
RibbonToolTip myRibbonToolTip = new RibbonToolTip();
myRibbonToolTip.Title = "test";
myRibbonSplitButton.ToolTip= myRibbonToolTip; 
Does not show a tooltip on mouseover, even though this technique works fine with other components such as RibbonButton and RibbonMenuButton.
